Modifications made by BlackKrait Technologies for the Nightjar project
(Apache License 2.0 section 4(b)): the voice (faster-whisper / kokoro-onnx),
vision, hybrid graph+vector memory, and Playwright browser modules were
extracted from Row-Bot and modified to remove all LangChain / LangGraph /
NiceGUI dependencies and orchestration, to run headless, and to be exposed
through a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server plus a WebSocket side-channel.
The embedding backend was changed from HuggingFace/torch to a local Ollama
embedding model. Each derived source file carries a header noting it is a
modified extract of the corresponding Row-Bot source.

